data.description: This charming 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom mobile home is situated on a 1-acre lot, providing ample space for your family and furry friends.For horse enthusiasts, the property has 5 horse pens and a horse run featuring a convenient lean-to in the back. Situated just outside the city limits of Joshua and within the Godley school district, this home offers the tranquility of rural living with the convenience of being close to the Chisholm Trail toll road, making it easy to commute. Large storage building in the back, currently serving as a feed room, provides plenty of space for storage and organization. Recently built carport, designed to be an enclosed building with roll-up doors and an attached carport in the front, is currently utilized as a carport. The possibilities are endless. Unwind after a long day on the covered back porch, where you can relish in the beauty of the surrounding countryside.
